{% extends "_base.njk" %}

{% block title %}
<div class"logo-word">Upcoming Events</div>
{% endblock %}


{% block content %}

<a name="event1"></a>
<div class ="event-page-item">
  <h3><a href= "https://www.facebook.com/events/1532067500207339/">New Activist Orientation</a></h3>
  <h4>Saturday, December 2nd</h4>
  <h4>6:30 pm - 9:00 pm</h4>
  <p>Do you care about animal suffering? Do you wish you had the power to do something about it? Join us and learn how YOU can make a difference for animals!</p>
  <p>Liberation Philly is creating a massive movement for animals this city. Based on the tactics of past social justice movement and social science, we aim to generate a crisis that can no longer be ignored.</p>
  <p>But we need YOU. Join us for this orientation and learn how you can get involved in the movement, and make a difference for animals.</p>
</div>

<a name="event2"></a>
<div class ="event-page-item">
  <h3><a href= "https://www.facebook.com/events/125710674790943/">Philly Farmed Animal Save - Slaughterhouse Vigil</a></h3>
  <h4>Saturday, December 16th</h4>
  <h4>4:00 pm - 6:00pm</h4>
  <h4>Saba Live Poultry</h4>
  <p>Join us in bearing witness and paying respect to just a few of the billions of lives losts. Signs and candles will be provided. Please wear black if possible. </p>
</div>
</div>

<a name="event3"></a>
<div class ="event-page-item">
  <h3><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/527040180990358/">Cube of Truth</a></h3>
  <h4>Sunday, December 10th</h4>
  <h4>1:00 pm - 3:00 pm</h4>
  <p>Liberation Philly is partnering with Anonymous for the Voiceless to bring the Cube of Truth to Philly!</p>
  <p>Join us in new monthly events in bringing awareness to public about the horrors of animal agriculture, and educating the community about a more compassionate lifestyle.</p>
  <p>All are welcome!</p>
</div>

<a name="event4"></a>
<div class ="event-page-item">
  <h3><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/290285748158876/">December Day of Action</a></h3>
  <h4>Saturday, December 23rd</h4>
  <h4>1:00 pm - 3:00 pm</h4>
  <p>"Peace on Earth and Goodwill for All" - right?</p>
  <p>Join us in a march through Center City as we raise awareness about the most oppressed, exploited, and forgotten individuals on our planet - individuals who have the same right to peace as all of us.</p>
  <p>We will meet at a location in Center City to be announced, and march through a popular downtown location. This will be a peaceful, non-violent demonstration with the goal of getting the issue of animal rights "on the table".</p>
</div>

<form method="post" id="subscribe-form" action="https://lists.liberationphilly.org/subscribe/campaigns">
